170 personnel and administrative functions of the commission.
171 (4) The Secretary of Energy shall be subject to the
172 ethics laws under Chapter 25 of Title 36.
173 (b) The commissionsecretary, under the provisions of
174 the merit systemMerit System, shall have the authority to
175 appoint or employ professional and administrative employees,
176 including attorneys, officers, and such accountants,
177 engineers, experts, inspectors, and other clerks and other
