322 Section 5. Notwithstanding Section 37-1-3(c), Code of
323 Alabama 1975, as amended by this act, the public service
324 commissioners serving on June 1, 2026, whose term ends after
325 the election held in November 2026 shall continue to serve
326 until January 18, 2027.
327 Section 6. Any reference in this act to a congressional
328 district shall refer to the congressional districts
